metadata.title: Precision Plunger Bars for Cartridge Grips – 93mm – Bag of 10 Plungers
features: Accepts cartridge needles with vice style tattoo machines
Works perfectly with Precision Disposable Soft Cartridge Grips
Price per one bag of 10 plungers
description: The Precision Plunger Bars are designed to work seamlessly with the Precision Disposable 1. 25" Contoured Soft Cartridge Grips and the Precision Disposable 1" Textured Soft Cartridge Grips to drive cartridge needles with vice style or standard tattoo machine setups. These plunger bars are manufactured from 304 Stainless Steel and feature a brass tip. The plungers are sold in a bag of ten in your choice of 88mm, 93mm, or 98mm length.
